folder: Fleet Street & Flatbush Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Fleet Street, south side, between Flatbush Ave., and Debevoise Place. A view of the Fleet Street M.E. Church, built In 1852, sold in 1921,
razed in 1923.
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
